* Was blind

40:42.140 --> 40:45.076
* But now

40:47.078 --> 40:51.149
* I see

40:52.951 --> 40:59.958
* 'Twas grace that taught

40:59.991 --> 41:05.063
* My heart to fear

41:06.164 --> 41:13.004
* And grace, my fears

41:13.672 --> 41:17.609
* Relieved

41:19.811 --> 41:26.317
* How precious did

41:26.351 --> 41:31.723
* That Grace appear

41:31.757 --> 41:37.696
* The hour I first

41:37.729 --> 41:42.100
* Believed

41:43.802 --> 41:50.108
* Amazing grace

41:50.141 --> 41:56.247
* How sweet the sound

41:56.281 --> 42:02.621
* That saved a wretch

42:02.654 --> 42:09.160
* Like me

42:09.194 --> 42:15.033
* I once was lost

42:15.066 --> 42:20.371
* But now am found

